<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    @page { size: A4; margin: 2cm 2.5cm; }
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #111; line-height: 1.55; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }

    /* ── En-tête lettre ── */
    .logo-name { font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; color: #1e3a5f; border-left: 4px solid #1e3a5f; padding-left: 8px; }
    .sender-info { font-size: 9pt; color: #444; padding-left: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .recipient-name { font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; color: #111; text-align: right; }
    .recipient-info { font-size: 9pt; color: #444; text-align: right; }
    .city-date { font-size: 9pt; color: #444; text-align: right; margin-top: 6px; }

    /* ── Objet ── */
    .objet { font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .objet strong { color: #1e3a5f; }

    hr { border: none; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; margin: 10px 0 14px 0; }

    /* ── Titre centré ── */
    h1 { font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #1e3a5f; margin: 0 0 4px 0; }
    .subtitle { text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; color: #555; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .ref-line { text-align: center; font-size: 8pt; color: #888; margin-bottom: 12px; }

    /* ── Tableaux montants ── */
    .sec { font-size: 9pt; font-weight: bold; color: #1e3a5f; border-left: 3px solid #1e3a5f; padding-left: 6px; margin: 12px 0 5px 0; }
    .amt td { padding: 4px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 10pt; }
    .amt td.r { text-align: right; }
    .amt tr.tot td { font-weight: bold; background: #eef2f7; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; }

    /* ── Statut paiement ── */
    .paid { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; font-weight: bold; padding: 6px 10px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; }
    .partial { background: #fef9c3; color: #b45309; font-weight: bold; padding: 6px 10px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; }

    /* ── Signature ── */
    .sign-box { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 9pt; }

    /* ── Pied ── */
    .legal { font-size: 7.5pt; color: #aaa; margin-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5; padding-top: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ── En-tête lettre (logo gauche / destinataire droite) ── -->
  <table style="margin-bottom: 14px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width: 52%; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 16px;">
        <div class="logo-name">LeComptoirImmo</div>
        <div class="sender-info">
          {% if payment.lease and payment.lease.parent_property %}
          {{ payment.lease.parent_property.name }}<br>
          {{ payment.lease.parent_property.full_address }}
          {% else %}
          Gestion locative
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </td>
      <td style="width: 48%; vertical-align: top; padding-left: 16px;">
        <div class="recipient-name">{{ payment.tenant.full_name if payment.tenant else '—' }}</div>
        <div class="recipient-info">
          {{ payment.unit.unit_ref if payment.unit else '' }}<br>
          {% if payment.lease and payment.lease.parent_property %}
          {{ payment.lease.parent_property.full_address }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="city-date">
          {% if payment.lease and payment.lease.parent_property and payment.lease.parent_property.city %}
          {{ payment.lease.parent_property.city }}, {% endif %}le {{ today }}
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- ── Objet ── -->
  <div class="objet">
    <strong>Objet :</strong> Quittance de loyer — {{ payment.period_label }}
  </div>

  <hr>

  <!-- ── Titre ── -->
  <h1>Quittance de loyer</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">{{ payment.period_label }}</p>
  <p class="ref-line">Réf. {{ payment.id | string | truncate(8, end='') }} — {{ payment.updated_at.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') }}</p>

  <!-- ── Loyer ── -->
  <div class="sec">Détail du loyer</div>
  <table class="amt">
    <tr><td>Loyer hors charges</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_rent | float) }} €</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Charges récupérables</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_charges | float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% if payment.amount_apl %}
    <tr><td>Déduction APL (tiers-payant CAF)</td><td class="r">- {{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_apl | float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% endif %}
    <tr class="tot"><td>Total dû par le locataire</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_due | float) }} €</td></tr>
  </table>

  <!-- ── Paiement reçu ── -->
  <div class="sec">Paiement reçu</div>
  <table class="amt">
    <tr><td>Montant encaissé</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_paid | float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% if payment.payment_date %}
    <tr><td>Date de réception</td><td class="r">{{ payment.payment_date.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') }}</td></tr>
    {% endif %}
    {% if payment.payment_method %}
    <tr><td>Mode de paiement</td><td class="r">
      {% if payment.payment_method == 'virement' %}Virement bancaire
      {% elif payment.payment_method == 'cheque' %}Chèque
      {% elif payment.payment_method == 'prelevement' %}Prélèvement automatique
      {% else %}Espèces{% endif %}
    </td></tr>
    {% endif %}
    {% if payment.balance > 0 %}
    <tr><td style="color:#b45309;">Solde restant dû</td><td class="r" style="color:#b45309;">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.balance) }} €</td></tr>
    {% endif %}
  </table>

  {% if payment.status == 'paid' %}
  <div class="paid">Loyer intégralement payé</div>
  {% elif payment.status == 'partial' %}
  <div class="partial">Paiement partiel</div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- ── Signature ── -->
  <table style="margin-top: 14px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width: 55%;"></td>
      <td style="width: 45%;">
        <div class="sign-box">
          <strong>Le bailleur</strong><br>
          Date : _______________<br><br>
          Signature :
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="legal">
    Quittance délivrée conformément à l'article 21 de la loi n°89-462 du 6 juillet 1989 tendant à améliorer les rapports locatifs.
    La présente quittance annule tous les reçus établis précédemment pour la même période. Document généré par LeComptoirImmo.
  </div>

</body>
</html>
